casebody.data:
Monday, September 26, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

94-988, 94-1246 and 94-1247. Ameritech Ohio v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, Nos. 93-1370-TP-ACE, 93-2069-TP-ACE and 93-2080-CT-ACE. These causes are pending before the court as appeals from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the joint motion for a stay of the briefing schedule and request for expedited ruling,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and the same is hereby, granted.
